_sText:
Hello guys.

Hopefully i could finish this map. The map has 3 standard levels (multibhop platforms) and 1 as bonus (no prespeed allowed).

It took me about 8 months to finish, because i didn't know how to make maps, and i didn't map during a long time. By the way the result is good and the gameplay is pretty fun. 

This is just a mid skilled bhop map. But maybe the bonus is pretty harder. Hope you enjoy, and tell me your opinion!!
